title: Trimble's 3 scores lead Indians past P.K. Yonge
text:
Trimble's 3 scores lead Indians past P.K. Yonge 
Sat, Oct 3, 2015 @ 12:09 am 
KEYSTONE HEIGHTS 19 
P.K. YONGE 14 
Ray Trimble scored all three TDs for the Indians (4-1, 1-0) in a District 3-4A victory over visiting P.K. Yonge (1-4, 0-2). ... Trimble caught an 18-yard TD pass from Wyatt Harvin and added scoring runs of 20 and 31 yards.
